sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Caller\n상위 호출자(미연결)
    participant E as Service\nengine.py\nscore_tests
    participant R as Service\ntests/registry.py\nget_scorer_for_test
    participant STS as Service\ntests/sts.py\nStsScorer.score
    participant G as Service\ntests/golden.py\nGoldenScorer.score
    participant U as Service\nbase.py\nUnsupportedScorer.score

    rect rgb(240,248,255)
    Note over C,E: 1) scoring 실행 시작\n입력: test_ids + ScoringContext\nScoringContext = { custom_test_id, custom_test_name, profile, answers, assessment_payload }
    C->>E: score_tests(test_ids, context)
    E->>E: results = {}
    end

    rect rgb(245,255,245)
    Note over E,R: 2) test_id 정규화 + scorer 선택 + score 호출
    loop 각 raw_test_id
        E->>E: raw_test_id -> str(...).strip().upper()
        alt test_id가 빈 값
            E->>E: continue
        else 유효한 test_id
            E->>R: get_scorer_for_test(test_id)
            R->>R: normalized = str(test_id).strip().upper()
            alt normalized == STS
                R-->>E: StsScorer()
                E->>STS: score(context)
                STS-->>E: ScoringResult\n{ status: not_implemented, test_id: STS, scales: {}, meta.message }
            else normalized == GOLDEN
                R-->>E: GoldenScorer()
                E->>G: score(context)
                G-->>E: ScoringResult\n{ status: not_implemented, test_id: GOLDEN, scales: {}, meta.message }
            else 기타 test_id
                R-->>E: UnsupportedScorer(test_id)
                E->>U: score(context)
                U-->>E: ScoringResult\n{ status: skipped, test_id, scales: {}, meta.reason=unsupported_test_id }
            end
            E->>E: results[test_id] = result
        end
    end
    end

    rect rgb(255,250,240)
    Note over E,C: 3) 결과 반환\n출력: dict[str, ScoringResult]
    E-->>C: { [test_id]: ScoringResult }
    end
